e=\"margin:6px 0 0;color:#5a6b63;\">Mineral-based cleaning agents that help address stains and water-related buildup.</p>\r\n          </div>\r\n\r\n          <div style=\"flex:1 1 360px;min-width:260px;background:#f7f3ed;border:1px solid #e3d6c7;border-radius:14px;padding:16px;\">\r\n            <p style=\"margin:0;font-weight:900;\">Polyvinyl Alcohol (PVA)</p>\r\n            <p style=\"margin:6px 0 0;color:#5a6b63;\">A water-soluble film that allows the sheet to dissolve completely during use.</p>\r\n          </div>\r\n\r\n          <div style=\"flex:1 1 360px;min-width:260px;background:#f7f3ed;border:1px solid #e3d6c7;border-radius:14px;padding:16px;\">\r\n            <p style=\"margin:0;font-weight:900;\">Glycerin</p>\r\n            <p style=\"margin:6px 0 0;color:#5a6b63;\">Helps maintain sheet structure and consistency.</p>\r\n          </div>\r\n\r\n          <div style=\"flex:1 1 360px;min-width:260px;background:#f7f3ed;border:1px solid #e3d6c7;border-radius:14px;padding:16px;\">\r\n            <p style=\"margin:0;font-weight:900;\">Polyether-Modified Polysiloxane</p>\r\n            <p style=\"margin:6px 0 0;color:#5a6b63;\">A surfactant that improves wetting and cleaning performance.</p>\r\n          </div>\r\n\r\n          <div style=\"flex:1 1 360px;min-width:260px;background:#f7f3ed;border:1px solid #e3d6c7;border-radius:14px;padding:16px;\">\r\n            <p style=\"margin:0;font-weight:900;\">Lemon Peel Oil</p>\r\n            <p style=\"margin:6px 0 0;color:#5a6b63;\">Provides a fresh citrus scent.</p>\r\n          </div>\r\n\r\n          <div style=\"flex:1 1 360px;min-width:260px;background:#f7f3ed;border:1px solid #e3d6c7;border-radius:14px;padding:16px;\">\r\n            <p style=\"margin:0;font-weight:900;\">Phenoxyethanol</p>\r\n            <p style=\"margin:6px 0 0;color:#5a6b63;\">Used in small amounts as a preservative to maintain product stability.</p>\r\n          </div>\r\n        </div>\r\n      </div>\r\n    </div>\r\n  </div>\r\n\r\n  